										<content:encoded><![CDATA[<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">The </span><a href="https://www.atfx.com.bz/en/live-chart/gbp-usd" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><span style="font-weight: 400;">GBPUSD</span></a><span style="font-weight: 400;"> exchange rate has moved above recent resistance but the market may move in the dollar’s favour. </span></p>
<p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-41358" src="https://www.atfx.com.bz/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/GBPUSD-Weekly-Chart.png" alt="GBPUSD - Weekly Chart" width="855" height="622" srcset="https://www.atfx.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/GBPUSD-Weekly-Chart.png 855w, https://www.atfx.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/GBPUSD-Weekly-Chart-300x218.png 300w, https://www.atfx.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/GBPUSD-Weekly-Chart-768x559.png 768w" sizes="(max-width: 855px) 100vw, 855px" /></p>
